<div class="cell grid-x" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
<div class="medium-18">
<div class="callout estimate-container" style="padding: 1rem; color: #000; display: none;">
<h3 id="estimate" style="color: #000; text-align: center;"></h3>
</div>
</div>
<div class="medium-18 medium-offset-1 success-1" style="display: none; margin-top: 20px;">
<p>The amount of the cost support may remain below EUR 2,000 which is the minimum amount that is paid. <b>However, please note that the amount given by this counter is not yet an official decision on the business cost support. The support needs to be applied separately via the e-services.</b></p>
</div>
<div class="medium-18 medium-offset-1 success-2" style="display: none; margin-top: 20px;">
<p>The amount of the cost support may be on the same scale as the amount provided by the counter. <b>However, please note that the amount given by this counter is not yet an official decision on the business cost support. The support needs to be applied separately via the e-services.</b></p>
</div>
